---
title: Cheat's Pork Jacket Potatoes with Sour Cream & Chives
description: Quick, grab your jacket! We’re flying out the door with this speedy take on taters in their jackets, complete with silky sour cream and our killer mince flavour hack.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b70fb3d30006c4732199586-4e258e56.jpg
